!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta(content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type")
  %body
    %h2 New comment on your "Win the World" article
    %p
    %p 
      Someone commented on an article that you (or your Home) wrote that was posted on the
      %a(href="http://wtw.familymembers.com") Win the world
      site.
    %br
    %p Article titled: #{h(@post.title)}
    %br
    %p Comment from: #{h(@comment.author)}.
    %p Country: #{@comment.country.blank? ? 'Unspecified' : h(@comment.country)}
    %p Email: #{@comment.email.blank? ? 'Unspecified' : h(@comment.email)}
    %p Posted on #{@comment.created_at.strftime("%d %B")}
    %br 
    = h(@comment.body)
    %br
    %br
    = link_to("Click here", @url) + " to see all the comments on the article. (If a question was asked, you may want to post a response.)"
    %br
    %p Have a great day! 
    %p Love, the Win the World team 
